{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":101,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"便让你们这对奸夫淫妇做对同命鸳鸯。","tone":"冷笑","chapter":56,"line_start":10,"line_end":12},{"speaker":"char_qi_yu","speaker_name":"齐雨","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"不要杀我，大爷曾答应过啊！","tone":"恳求","chapter":56,"line_start":14,"line_end":14},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"少龙！我对不起你，也配不起你，杀了我吧！","tone":"悲痛","chapter":56,"line_start":20,"line_end":22},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"我不想让你这淫妇污了项某人的宝剑。","tone":"冷酷","chapter":56,"line_start":24,"line_end":25},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"记得吗？我曾说过任何人要杀死本人，都要付出惨痛代价，现在我就证明给你看，叫你的王兄和赵穆来吧！","tone":"愤怒","chapter":56,"line_start":25,"line_end":28},{"speaker":"char_zhao_ya","speaker_name":"赵雅","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"你不是要逃出去吗？","tone":"疑问","chapter":56,"line_start":30,"line_end":30},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"当然！我现在立即走，有了朱姬，我已可向秦王交代。","tone":"得意","chapter":56,"line_start":32,"line_end":34},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":null,"text":"糟了！给发觉哩！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":56,"line_start":38,"line_end":38},{"speaker":"char_wu_zhuo","speaker_name":"乌卓","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"没时间哩！先回城堡去。","tone":"焦急","chapter":56,"line_start":40,"line_end":40},{"speaker":"char_qi_yu","speaker_name":"齐雨","listener":"char_zhao_ya","text":"看！赵兵来了，我们有救哩！","tone":"欣喜","chapter":56,"line_start":44,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_wu_shi_luo","speaker_name":"乌氏倮","listener":"char_zhu_ji","text":"夫人，应是高兴的时候才对。","tone":"欣慰","chapter":56,"line_start":60,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_zhu_ji","speaker_name":"朱姬","listener":"char_wu_shi_luo","text":"我们母子得有今天，全仗乌爷豪情厚义，感激的话不说了，只要我们母子一天在秦国还可以说话，便要保得你们乌家富贵荣华、子孙昌盛。","tone":"感激","chapter":5