{"segment":2,"line_start":102,"line_end":202,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wu_zhuo","speaker_name":"乌卓","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"当众折辱一下他也好！","tone":"调侃","chapter":56,"line_start":103,"line_end":103},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":null,"text":"叫他有屁就放吧！","tone":"调侃","chapter":56,"line_start":105,"line_end":105},{"speaker":"char_wu_zhuo","speaker_name":"乌卓","listener":null,"text":"有屁就放！","tone":"大笑","chapter":56,"line_start":109,"line_end":109},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_zhuo","text":"为何他们不把护城河的水源截断，那样就不用涉水过河那么麻烦了呀！","tone":"疑问","chapter":56,"line_start":135,"line_end":137},{"speaker":"char_wu_zhuo","speaker_name":"乌卓","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"我们这条是活河，不用引进河水，因为壕底有泉水喷出，想截断也不可能。","tone":"陈述","chapter":56,"line_start":139,"line_end":141},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"破解之法，是开凿支流，把河水引走，那最少要十多天的时间才成，我猜他们正在后方赶建浮桥，横跨河上，方便攻城。","tone":"平静","chapter":56,"line_start":145,"line_end":147},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_teng_yi","text":"那现在下面这些人岂非只是虚张声势？","tone":"疑问","chapter":56,"line_start":149,"line_end":149},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"围城军最忌闷围，必须让他们有些动作，当作活动筋骨也好，操练也好，只有如此才能保持士气。","tone":"陈述","chapter":56,"line_start":151,"line_end":153},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":null,"text":"准备沙石！灭火队候命。","tone":"厉声","chapter":56,"line_start":161,"line_end":163}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
